    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Art Nouveau movement in Poland including the visual arts, literature, and music. The group of artists involved in the movement were active ca. 1890/1918.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
